(1) For every licence to be a gold broker or factor there shall be paid a fee of one thousand two hundred and fifty fee units, and every such licence shall be issued by the Minister and shall be in Form 2 in the Schedule : Provided that every such licence shall, no matter when taken out, expire on the 31st December then next following.
